<h2>New Claim Submitted - Review Required</h2>

<p>Hello {{adminName}},</p>

<p>A new claim has been submitted and requires your review.</p>

<div class="info-box">
    <h3>Claim Details</h3>
    <table class="info-table">
        <tr>
            <td>Claim Number:</td>
            <td><strong>{{claimNumber}}</strong></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Claimant Name:</td>
            <td>{{claimantName}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Claim Type:</td>
            <td>{{claimType}}</td>
        </tr>
        {{#if claimAmount}}
        <tr>
            <td>Claim Amount:</td>
            <td>{{formatCurrency claimAmount}}</td>
        </tr>
        {{/if}}
        <tr>
            <td>Submitted Date:</td>
            <td>{{formatDateTime submittedAt}}</td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</div>

<div class="alert alert-warning">
    <h4>Action Required</h4>
    <p>Please review this claim and take appropriate action:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Review submitted documents and information</li>
        <li>Verify claim validity and coverage</li>
        <li>Approve or reject the claim</li>
        <li>Request additional information if needed</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="alert alert-info">
    <h4>How to Process</h4>
    <ol>
        <li>Log into the SDK Admin Portal</li>
        <li>Navigate to "Claims" section</li>
        <li>Find the claim with number: {{claimNumber}}</li>
        <li>Review all submitted documents and information</li>
        <li>Update claim status and add notes as needed</li>
    </ol>
</div>

<p>Please process this claim within 48 hours to maintain good customer service.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>
<strong>SDK Admin Portal Claims Team</strong></p> 